# ====================================================================================================================================
# CATEGORY : MAPS
# ====================================================================================================================================
# Covers all Map Printing regression packs for the BISS internal (staff) portal:
#   TC_01 - Map generation by herd number search
#   TC_02 - Map generation by parcel number search, incl. every required-field validation
#   TC_03 - Generated map metadata and pagination
#   TC_04 - Partnership herd maps and download
#   TC_05 - Maps surfaced on the Correspondence screen
#   TC_10 - Map download from the generated maps table
#   TC_11 - Parcel search format tolerance
#
# DATA
#   Herds, parcels and references are resolved from the DB at runtime by the @staffdata hook
#   via DBRouter. Features never name a herd index - "the next submitted herd" pops the next
#   unused value from the resolved list, so sections stay independent and re-runnable.
#   Staff accounts (agr11612 / agr2332 / agr4442 / agr5033) are hardcoded permission
#   fixtures, not test data - each carries a specific role the test depends on.
#
# STEP DEFINITIONS : MapPrintingSteps.java (stepdefinitions.STAFF)
# LOCATORS         : ObjectRepository.properties - Section: Map Printing
# Author           : Aniket Pathare | aniket.pathare@government.ie
# Created          : 15-07-2026
